{
  "stem": "10768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the wives will later find out where they went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remain in Katowice for, as I said, to the end or beginning of December.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remained there until I noticed that since the town was already like a ghost town and I felt that there is no place for me to remain, and even when I-- I was able to take a train from Katowice to Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had a German friend my own age, who was very nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And since my name was Wielopolska, she made out for me a pass.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I was able to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the trains were running between Katowice and Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went several times to Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went there for Saturday, usually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was talking over with the family what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, at that time, had no other place to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was their home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I, myself, since I saw that there is a trend of a lot of young people who, perhaps, had some left leanings-- leaned, maybe, you know, socialist-- that a lot of them felt that the German territory's too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's better to go to the Russian territory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a trend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, myself, didn't have this in mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my parents were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt my function is finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever I had to do and whatever, however I could help these relatives while we were running together away, that now is my time to go back to my parents.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "While I was in Katowice during these three years or four years-- no, more than four years-- I was, besides work, I was trying to study because in our town, Lesko-- Lesko didn't have a gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
